&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit an , enthusiastic and motivated medical secretary/ personal assistant to join our friendly team and provide full secretarial support within the ENT department at Queen Elizabeth Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ENT Department is a busy and demanding department. We are looking for an individual who can prioritise their own workload, has excellent communication and interpersonal skills and can work under pressure and as part of a team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate should be educated to GCSE standard or equivalent and should either possess the AMSPAR Diploma or have had significant experience as a Band 4 medical secretary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Informal enquiries are welcome. Please contact Jayne Orme, Team Leader via email or direct 0121 371 4812&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post is on a 12 month fixed term contract due to funding for the department &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Interview Date: tbc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
